00:13:56.220 --> 00:13:58.480
Maliban sa imperial forbidden grounds,

00:13:58.480 --> 00:13:59.410
lahat ng iba pang lugar

00:13:59.790 --> 00:14:01.590
ay lubusang hinanap.

00:14:02.190 --> 00:14:03.260
Ang imperial forbidden grounds

00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:05.340
wag mo lang isama yung villa ko.

00:14:05.730 --> 00:14:07.800
Bakit hindi mo pinaghihinalaan ang Kanyang Kamahalan

00:14:08.150 --> 00:14:09.680
o ang Retiradong Emperador?

00:14:10.140 --> 00:14:12.790
Dahil lang sa kinain ng Kanyang Kamahalan
ang gintong peach

00:14:12.990 --> 00:14:14.720
at inatake ng raptor,

00:14:14.790 --> 00:14:15.600
habang ako

00:14:16.040 --> 00:14:18.500
kumain ng gintong peach
at nanatiling hindi nasaktan?

00:14:18.750 --> 00:14:20.140
Kaya naniniwala ka rin sa mga iyon

00:14:20.140 --> 00:14:21.780
walang basehang tsismis

00:14:22.360 --> 00:14:24.060
at pinaghihinalaan ang sarili mong ina?

