Lahat ng lalaki mula sa Yongzhou Prefecture

00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:14.609
ay na-deploy na.

00:17:14.640 --> 00:17:16.400
Naibigay na namin ang lahat ng 110 distrito ng Chang'an

00:17:16.400 --> 00:17:17.720
at ang mga nakapaligid na county

00:17:17.720 --> 00:17:18.720
isang masusing paghahanap

00:17:18.829 --> 00:17:19.550
ngunit hindi pa rin mahanap

00:17:19.550 --> 00:17:21.079
Ang kinaroroonan ni Scholar Su.

00:17:21.160 --> 00:17:23.359
Ako rin ay labis na nababalisa tungkol dito.

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:24.770
Salamat, Opisyal na Wu.

00:17:24.790 --> 00:17:25.849
Hindi na kailangan ng salamat.

00:17:26.510 --> 00:17:28.040
Sa pamamagitan ni Empress Wu Zetian,

00:17:28.109 --> 00:17:29.640
magkamag-anak talaga kami.

00:17:30.110 --> 00:17:31.270
Lu, ang iyong pagkakakilanlan

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:32.680
ay hindi na sikreto.

00:17:33.030 --> 00:17:34.070
Sa iyong pagbabalik sa kabisera,

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:36.070
tiyak na mabilis kang tataas sa ranggo.

00:17:37.270 --> 00:17:39.790
Sana maalala mo ako sa hinaharap.

00:17:42.200 --> 00:17:43.400
Walang problema

00:17:43.720 --> 00:17:44.750
meron ako

00:17:45.650 --> 00:17:47.220
isang maliit na kahilingan.

00:17:47.550 --> 00:17:48.680
Sige lang, Lu.

00:17:49.310 --> 00:17:51.900
Dahil alam mo ang aking pagkatao,

00:17:52.440 --> 00:17:53.750
dapat maintindihan mo

00:17:54.110 --> 00:17:56.400
na Cen Zhi,
Commander ng Prinsesa Guard, at ako

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.470
ay matalik na kaibigan.

00:17:57.470 --> 00:17:58.010
[Yongzhou Prefecture]

00:17:58.010 --> 00:17:58.880
Ang kanyang katawan

00:17:58.880 --> 00:18:00.920
dapat itago
sa Yongzhou Prefecture, tama ba?

00:18:00.920 --> 00:18:02.520
Nagdala ako ng isang baso ng alak.

00:18:02.550 --> 00:18:03.440
Gusto ko siyang makita

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:04.570
at bigyan mo ng respeto

00:18:04.570 --> 00:18:06.200
bilang kaibigan niya.

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:09.660
tiyak.

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:11.020
Walang problema.

00:18:52.830 --> 00:18:53.560
Lu Lingfeng,

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:55.320
hindi ka natulog kagabi?

00:18:57.470 --> 00:18:58.640
Natulog ka na ba

00:18:59.310 --> 00:19:00.970
simula nang mawala si Su Wuming?

00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:01.690
ako...

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:05.670
masama na ba ang itsura ko ngayon?

00:19:09.850 --> 00:19:10.960
Isang taong gumagamit ng tapat na puso

00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:12.240
para alagaan ang iba

00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:14.230
ay laging maganda.

00:19:16.410 --> 00:19:16.840
Master!

00:19:16.840 --> 00:19:19.120
[Maaaring dalhin ng dakilang birtud ang mundo]

00:19:21.060 --> 00:19:21.960
Si Su Wuming ay nawawala

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:22.740
para sa 16 na oras.

00:19:23.210 --> 00:19:24.350
Ang ebidensya na meron tayo

00:19:24.370 --> 00:19:25.300
ay napakalimitado.

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:27.360
Handa akong magtiwala kay Fei.

00:19:27.810 --> 00:19:29.790
I bet na ang raptor ay nasa Mount Zhongnan.

00:19:29.790 --> 00:19:30.590
may plano ako,

00:19:30.890 --> 00:19:31.750
ngunit ito ay mapanganib.

00:19:32.310 --> 00:19:32.970
Samakatuwid,

00:19:33.830 --> 00:19:35.890
Mananatili si Xue Huan para pangalagaan si Fei.

00:19:35.980 --> 00:19:36.880
Master, ano?

00:19:37.440 --> 00:19:38.350
Kung ito ay mapanganib,

00:19:38.350 --> 00:19:39.750
hindi ba dapat manatili si Miss Xijun?

00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:40.640
Hindi siya marunong martial arts.

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:41.510
Tumigil sa pagtatalo.

00:19:42.280 --> 00:19:43.680
Inutusan kitang manatili.

00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:46.680
Oo.

00:19:48.110 --> 00:19:48.640
Tara na.

