Anong ginawa ko dun?

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:43.350
Ano kaya ang maaari kong gawin?

00:24:43.350 --> 00:24:44.920
Hindi ko ito ginulo o inistorbo.

00:24:44.920 --> 00:24:46.130
Bigla itong nabalisa.

00:24:46.130 --> 00:24:47.860
Akala ko kakainin ako nito!

00:24:47.880 --> 00:24:49.540
Hindi man lang ako kumain ng peach.

00:24:49.590 --> 00:24:50.510
Kung hindi mo sasabihin sa akin,

00:24:50.510 --> 00:24:51.600
papatayin kita!

00:24:56.360 --> 00:24:57.520
Tapos sige.

00:24:58.400 --> 00:25:00.620
Namatay sa villa ng Retired Emperor

00:25:01.020 --> 00:25:02.610
ay magiging isang pagpapala

00:25:02.750 --> 00:25:04.000
para sa akin.

00:25:04.720 --> 00:25:06.370
Paano mo malalaman kung saan ito?

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:08.030
nahulaan ko.

00:25:08.750 --> 00:25:09.790
Hayaan akong magpaliwanag

00:25:09.790 --> 00:25:10.880
kung paano ko nalaman.

00:25:10.880 --> 00:25:11.960
Walang oras para diyan!

00:25:12.570 --> 00:25:13.910
Kapag nahanap ko na,

00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:15.240
ang una kong gagawin

00:25:15.240 --> 00:25:16.720
kainin na ba kita!

00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:27.650
[Kapayapaan at kaunlaran]

00:25:49.220 --> 00:25:50.510
[Eleganteng katahimikan]

00:26:03.090 --> 00:26:04.550
Isang knockout na gamot.

00:26:04.830 --> 00:26:06.390
Mas marami mas mabuti.

00:26:06.590 --> 00:26:08.530
Kung mapapatumba nito agad ang isang tao,

00:26:08.530 --> 00:26:10.530
tiyak na magpapatumba ito ng ibon.

00:26:31.070 --> 00:26:31.680
Xijun,

00:26:32.150 --> 00:26:33.010
itago mo ang sarili mo.

00:26:52.630 --> 00:26:53.920
Mula ngayon,

00:26:54.470 --> 00:26:56.690
kukuha ka ng mga order mula kay Lu Lingfeng.

00:26:57.240 --> 00:26:57.750
Siya

00:26:58.400 --> 00:26:59.600
kinakatawan ako!

